      "@id": "self-service-policy-exemptions-defender-for-cloud",
      "@type": "Decision",
      "decision": "Defender for Cloud recommendations that require a paid SKU are exempted by the platform.",
      "why": "The platform's security appetite does not require paid SKUs — recommendations with no free remediation path are exempted rather than left as unactionable noise.",
